QuestData.Title: Work Order: The August Celestials I
QuestData.Description: <Yoon's familiar writing scrolls across the tattered paper.>$b$bThe trainees out at the Cradle of Chi-Ji are in need of striped melons. Apparently, they use them in their training exercises.$b$bA representative will be by tomorrow to collect whatever striped melons you can spare.
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant 8 Striped Melon Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
